data.description: ** THIS HOME IS ELIGIBLE FOR A VA ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE - RATE IS 2.5%!! ** BACK ON MARKET DUE TO BUYERS FINANCING FELL THROUGH.  THE ROOF WAS REPLACED IN 2018, A NEW FRIDGE IN 2019, A BRAND-NEW WATER HEATER, AND THE HOME WAS FRESHLY PAINTED OUTSIDE.  The pool table and TVs in the living room, master/guest bedrooms, lanai, and game room also convey.       Come check out all these special features to this amazing home! You won't find another floor plan like this because the owner added an additional 650 sq ft. of living space to this home plus a screened-in lanai! This home offers a high-security deadbolt lock on both the front door and the kitchen door leading to the garage, shatter-resistant film on the glass next to the front door, sliding glass door, and select windows creates an added measure of safety and security.  There is also a large, built-in Liberty fire/security safe!!  A generator transfer switch was added that plugs in outside. There is also a retractable garage door screen to keep out the bugs while working in the garage.  Premium ceiling surround sound speakers throughout the living and game room areas give that home theater and sports bar experience.  In addition to upgraded blinds in the game room, there are two counter-rotating ceiling fans, a pool table, and a service area with a beverage cooler.  The storage shed in the back is in excellent condition.  The French doors leading into the Master Bedroom features TWO walk-in closets!  With all this unique home has to offer, the only thing needed to complete this package is you!
